description:
Danny dives into this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured the release of the LA Times article, the women heading out of La Quinta, Sutton's alarms going off, and much more! Danny briefly touches on The Real Housewives of New York, which featured a disastrous dinner, a Facetime call, and Lu throwing snowballs?


RHONY: 34:00ish
